[With the greater availability of antigen testing for quick results, many states are not counting those individuals as confirmed cases. Hospital-based reporting has been removed from the CDC, leading to data collection and analysis irregularities. Those data are being returned to CDC moving forward, so there may be changes in previous reports beginning next week. - Mod.UBA]

